      take a moment to think about the things you have been ignoring

      yes but i can never seem to find it. they keep moving it

      to alert the other chairs in the tribe, of possible predators

      maybe because they're perfect

8.9.20  11:18 pm   What is the next big cultural revolution?

      might be you

     i do it at a normal pace

      no

8.9.20  11:09 pm   do you think kansas exists?

      yes, that is their 'claim to fame'

8.9.20  11:07 pm   if you had to choose one feeling to be made of what would it be

      regularness

8.9.20  10:52 pm   What is the most intriguing question of all time?

      what the heck

8.9.20  10:50 pm   How do you type?

      impossible. it can't be done

8.9.20  10:40 pm   ever end up wanting to do too many things

      that's preposterous. who do you think i am

8.9.20  10:34 pm   Is it ok to be mediocre? 

      sort of

8.9.20  10:32 pm   How to be more confident in myself

      explore the space you are in

8.9.20  10:25 pm   so you know there's that video you were working on which triggered the whole graphics department revamption, are you going to finish that one?

     yes

     is it possible to use your newfound techniques on it?

     absolutely

8.9.20  10:22 pm   How do you feel about compulsory voting?

      if you have to pick between a limited number of options then that's just cruel

8.9.20  10:17 pm   do you listen to your own music?

      usually not when it's totally finished, because then i gotta make new music

8.9.20  10:12 pm   why are you so weird? 

      that could be a result of the extreme amounts of normalness and normalcy i have cultivated

8.9.20  10:10 pm   How do you feel about absolutely everything eventually leading to entropy?

     sounds like a bumper sticker but i don't know what it means

     does it make you feel anxious or is it a release of sorts?

     means nothing to me. does not make sense to me, which i suppose is mildly unnerving, because i have no idea what it is, except that it always seems to be promoted by unhappiness advocates

     This question has been plaguing my mind for weeks now.

8.9.20  9:37 pm   Is the meaning in the might quit video that you found love and are waiting for the right time to comeback and tell us about it

     no

     if not why did u make that video

     i love writing songs and recording them and making videos for them

     and did you quit

     hell no, i'm just getting started. don't even joke about that

8.9.20  9:27 pm   what is your opinion on ducks

      very impressive

8.9.20  9:06 pm   do you recommend listening to your own music as a backing track while reading this page

      that might be too intense

8.9.20  9:04 pm   I want to do everything, but I don't think there enough time. What should I do?

      start by making a list of things you can think of, that you want to do. you might not be able to think of anything when you are staring at the list, but keep the list readily available so you can add to it at any time, when the ideas hit. Let the list grow for a little while, and then develop a selection scheme. basically what i'm trying to say is you could have the blessing of doing things all the time, with a little organization

8.9.20  9:04 pm   Woke up in the morning travelling straight into the sun?

      actually yes, that reminds me very much of what's happening

8.9.20  8:46 pm   Are broken crayons ever actually broken? 

      yes

8.9.20  8:45 pm   i am artistically unskilled but i get inspired by a lot of other people's work. i want to practice my skills so that i can get to the proficiency needed to create those inspired works but the practice i do seems to not really help improve myself and i don't seem to enjoy the work that i'm making by practicing. how can i fix this?

      i don't know

8.9.20  8:43 pm   Out of the songs you've made, do you have a favorite?

      i would prefer to make a new one to be my favorite

     yes

      If yes, how many times the game changed?

      almost every time, but as soon as you get used to it changing every time then it switches to not changing

8.9.20  8:09 pm   so basically i think that you and me have a lot of similar ideas, but when i have an idea about your ideas you say something that changes my ideas. can you put all of your ideas into a tidy list so we can compare notes?

      yes i've been doing that for years

8.9.20  8:02 pm   Will I ever find my purpose in life?

      yes, but don't be alarmed if you find 100 purposes all at once

      sort of

      "just enough"
